  m_Text: Step into a mysterious industrial base in the heart of a futuristic city,
    where out-of-control machines threaten the entire system. You'll control a robotic
    warrior, navigating dangerous areas, dodging obstacles, and battling a variety
    of enemies. Collect items, uncover hidden stories, and hone your skills to delve
    deeper into the base. With classic pixel art, a fast pace, and a sci-fi atmosphere,
    the game delivers challenging and engaging 2D action.
